may peace be upon you,
The name of this mosque is Baby Wali Mosque. Another name of this mosque is (Abdullah Baig). There are five daily prayers in this mosque. In this mosque there is a neem tree. And there is a shrine. And the mosque building is very old. There is also a water bore in the mosque. There is also an Ashura Khana in the wing of the mosque. A small part of the mosque is leased out to run Alamein High School.
